<P>&startq;I am wor&s;e!&endq; &s;he cried faintly, &startq;my wi&s;h
comes fa&s;t upon me! Ah! not for my puni&s;hment let
it finally arrive!&endq;</P>
<P>With terror, however, even more than with malady,
