<P>&startq;Accident, my deare&s;t Mother,&mdash;$el$ding appear|ances,
&mdash;and fal&s;e internal rea&s;oning on my part.&mdash;and
on his, continual mi&s;con&s;truction! O my deare&s;t Mo|ther!
