<P>&startq;There was another letter, too!&endq; interrupted
Camilla, with quick blu&s;hing recollection;&mdash;&startq;but
my illne&s;s&mdash;and all that has followed, made me
forget them both till this very moment&mdash;Did &s;he
&s;ay any thing of any&mdash;other?&endq;</P>
<P>&startq;Yes;&mdash;the other had been delivered accord|ing
